Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.25,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}FLYING IN THE SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:09.19,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最高的地方 馳騁於空中的任何角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.92,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:16.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮大地的盡頭呼喚奇跡的咒語 {\fnComic Sans MS}SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:25.44,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不遲疑的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:31.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有無限的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:39.08,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論嘗試多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:47.51,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼痛苦都貫徹到底{\fnComic Sans MS}（G GUNDAM）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:50.63,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛隨時都充斥於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.21,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:57.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手 咆哮著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.31,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向明天飛奔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.10,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}BRIGHT YOU NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所描繪的未來之藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.80,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.60,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:15.34,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部如你所願 {\fnComic Sans MS}I GET A CHANCE！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I WOULD LIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IF I MAY TO TAKE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OH，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請容我講解GUNDAM FIGHT的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那起源自60年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開被極度污染的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛上宇宙的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免衛星國家之間爆發全面戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是創立每四年一度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各國派出代表的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱名為GUNDAM的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以FIGHT的方式不斷戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後勝出的GUNDAM代表的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能得到衛星國家聯邦的主導權
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然創出充滿體育精神的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，餘下的問題有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項FIGHT的舞台是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，就是我們居住的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被極度污染的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，今屆大賽看來有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的人，你有見過這男人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這照片會掀起多猛烈的戰鬥風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的對手是neo America的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·庫羅克特的Gundam Maxter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs56}咆哮吧！抓緊夢想的必殺重拳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo America的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽聽這些歡呼聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，會變得一片死寂的紐約
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經重新充滿著生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而理由只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Maxter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo America的Mobile Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機體以一擊便把我們的宿敵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史格特GUNDAM打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在那身體內難以估計的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌駕世界各國的GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年，neo America會實現我們的宿願
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回GUNDAM FIGHT的冠軍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，操縱這部Gundam Maxter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們光榮的戰土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·庫羅克特！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒萬丈的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，我們一起呼喚他的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·庫羅克特…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了，我回到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，這裡是我夢想的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在，我以Gundam Fighter的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊夢想的時候來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這隻手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧！全世界的Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓任何人凌駕在我之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I AM CHAMPION！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘，你和那男人是深交嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，以前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是這一帶出名的頑皮仔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，他飛上衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經實現了夢想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為強者後能住在衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能成為英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他是我們的希望之星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何要打倒這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你也去看冠軍爭奪戰吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球和衛星的宇宙統一比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠軍爭奪戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你打消這種娛樂節目的念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一擊便把其中一名FIGHT選手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Italy的Neros Gundam打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Japan的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情報說他已潛入曼克頓這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING GUNDAM 算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種日本人不是我的對手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在或許也在打你主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，你們國防總省會保護我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我有這班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬能的女孩子保護我便夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HAPPY！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星冠軍算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙怎會贏到我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像夢一樣的宇宙統一比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是世紀之戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百戰百勝的衛星冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·庫羅克特入場了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任由他得意忘形沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是時勢所逼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他順利勝出GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後回去領功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前，他是我們的明星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後，他默默無聞而終
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成星塵也不要緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很卑鄙啊！犯規呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是冠軍！是另一個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Japan的Gundam Fighter…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,King Of Heart，多蒙·卡休！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·庫羅克特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你進行GUNDAM FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該不能拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真是neo America的英雄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混悵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼！還不快去捉住他！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT，我已經向你提出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！不要走！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪無可恕！竟敢戲弄我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪，你冷靜一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他令我在眾人前丟臉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我出生的這個故鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟他決一高下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芭妮，給我查出他的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，GUNDAM FIGHT…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉陪啊，告訴他時間和地點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫羅克特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你把那工作交給我們去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一發現他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的暗殺部隊便會行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多管閒事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟他在GUNDAM FIGHT裡決一高下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我講…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是眼中釘啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，你加倍努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會說的臭小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒倚靠他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今，我要不擇手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為只是擦過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不愧是Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三名持槍的男子嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很棘手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位，給電槍擊中也會很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這種地方做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想全部由這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時非常貧窮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼了命在這城市生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每日過著孤獨而無助的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對從未見過的宇宙衛星懷著夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只管想著我要成為強者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在市內不停搗亂的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給政府高層的人看中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我終能看見衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候，我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想是要親手去抓緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我要試試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在GUNDAM FIGHT裡勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓自己成為這城市的人的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了那志向，夢想便不只是夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用這雙拳頭來證明！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧！日本人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，什麼地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是紐約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商業區的破舊酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，我是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估…中…了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心有後後遺症
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以防萬一的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你真的要小心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在這城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有憑實力才能表現自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫奇波迪的有點不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪有口訊給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他接受你的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八時在百老匯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺多蒙·卡休失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人幫了我很大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的照計劃進行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡過頭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙先行一步了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，究竟是什麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了約定時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Japan的戰士還未在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯克林運動場出現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說在百老匯…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，多蒙他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？日本人，你怕了我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，他在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是你的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？那裡應該是無人地區啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·庫羅克特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然利用女人來欺騙多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了！道格拉斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想我丟臉到什麼時候！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉，我們去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動掃瞄系統開動！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺了你領功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後飛上衛星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來跟你決一高下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點坐進GUNDAM裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動掃瞄系統開動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦波、血壓、心跳、呼吸、體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新陳代謝機能全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在那種地方裡！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NICE，日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪！你打算做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是幫你的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你令neo America丟盡臉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今，我連你也收拾！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然情況糟透
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我重新向你挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯接受嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT，READY！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？我的力量不及他！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·庫羅克特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識這男人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑！現在是比賽中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種人沒有理由會認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OH！MY GOD！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？快點了結我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算同情我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這次輪到我令這城市丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，這樣，我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也隨著這條臂完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪！站起來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你！再次站起來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我們的夢想啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你！不要輸啊！奇波迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT國際條約第三條
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有奪取冠軍的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了多少次也能重新振作參加比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這城市重頭來過便行…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，永不氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為這城市奪回夢想便行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我這只拳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I WILL BE BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休，今日我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終有一日會報仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·庫羅克特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NICE GUY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THANK YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:30.50,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便數千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:34.89,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:39.33,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨著 追求著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:42.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:50.05,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人啊 在我瞳孔的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:55.75,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實搖曳著的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:23:01.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何傳達才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:07.54,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓受傷的心與身體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:11.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這溫暖的懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:17.71,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比海更深沉的睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
